  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently we have bitwise_lmd_ghost which as an optimised fork choice rule. This will be useful in phase 1 of the spec. Currently we require an optimised version of lmd-ghost for phase 0. This can be easily created from bitwise-lmd-ghost by modifying the `choose_best_child` function: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/8671c5790c453a9a945469baa4f15c4a8157956b/eth2/fork_choice/src/bitwise_lmd_ghost.rs#L206 \r\nto simply select the child that has the most votes, rather than performing the search over the binary hash. \r\n\r\nThis new fork-choice should be created as  a new algorithm in the `ForkChoiceAlgorithms` enum. \r\n\r\nIf you are interested in taking up this issue, hit up @AgeManning on gitter for more detailed info :). \r\n",
